Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.18,0:00:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\fs22\shad1\c&H70D8FB&\fn迷你简汉真广标\b0\pos(312,420)}漫迪字幕组倾情奉献\N\N——·乜可里译制·——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.44,0:00:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我都干了些什么? 天啊 我干了些什么\N{\fnArial\fs18}What have I done? Oh, God, what have I done...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.85,0:00:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的 Jake\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's all right, Jake.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.26,0:01:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会陪你度过难关的\N{\fnArial\fs18}We'll get through this as a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.34,0:01:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,对啊 别担心了 爸爸\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yeah, don't worry, Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.47,0:01:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,无论发生什么事 你还有我们啊\N{\fnArial\fs18}We're here for you no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.13,0:01:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我快要错过"将到美景"了\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm going to miss Upcoming Attractions!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.78,0:01:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么事了?\N{\fnArial\fs18}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.95,0:01:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你爸在生意上遇到些小挫折 亲爱的\N{\fnArial\fs18}Your father had a little business setback, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.59,0:01:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他失去了一个客户\N{\fnArial\fs18}He lost a client.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.35,0:01:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,他说"我有个很棒的主意"\N{\fnArial\fs18}"I got a great idea," he said
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.65,0:01:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,"一个价值百万美元的主意"\N{\fnArial\fs18}"A million dollar idea," he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.31,0:01:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,他说"给宠物抽的雪茄 你怎么看?"\N{\fnArial\fs18}"Cigars for pets. What do you think?" he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.12,0:01:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他说"我希望你可以老实回答"\N{\fnArial\fs18}"I want you to be honest," he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.66,0:01:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我特么地居然信他说实话了\N{\fnArial\fs18}What the hell made me believe him?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.91,0:01:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Jake 每个人都有说错话的时候\N{\fnArial\fs18}Jake, everyone slips up now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.47,0:01:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他因为说实话把你解雇了?\N{\fnArial\fs18}He fired you for being honest?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.43,0:01:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一个圈套\N{\fnArial\fs18}It was entrapment!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.62,0:01:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,就是说我和Qunin再也不用去那运动鞋血汗工厂咯?\N{\fnArial\fs18}So it's off to the sneaker sweatshop for me and Quinn?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.45,0:01:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你们两个别胡扯了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Don't be ridiculous, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.32,0:01:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria 你知道我已经有很多事够忙的了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Daria, you know I've got more work than I can handle,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.28,0:01:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你会再忙起来的 Jacky\N{\fnArial\fs18}and you'll get busy again, Jakey.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.97,0:01:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,只要再耐心等待一下\N{\fnArial\fs18}Just be patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.50,0:01:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那等的同时我要做什么呢?\N{\fnArial\fs18}But what'll I do in the meantime?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.99,0:01:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是总说你想要做烹饪嘛?\N{\fnArial\fs18}You always said you want to work on your cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.50,0:01:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想找点事让自己忙起来的话\N{\fnArial\fs18}If you're looking for some way to occupy yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.85,0:01:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那里还有很多需要做的家务活\N{\fnArial\fs18}there are plenty of chores that need doing around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.86,0:01:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了? 是你先说起的\N{\fnArial\fs18}What? You get to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.29,0:01:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fnArial\fs18}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.09,0:02:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Brittany 你挤颜料了吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Brittany, did you spill your paint?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.84,0:02:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,没有?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Um, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.12,0:02:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,请问现在方便吗 Defoe老师?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Is this a good time, Ms. Defoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.03,0:02:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,方便 进来吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yes, come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.65,0:02:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,同学们 Li校长和O'Neill先生有些激动人心的事要告诉我们\N{\fnArial\fs18}Class, Ms. Li and Mr. O'Neill have some intriguing news.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.30,0:02:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我们朗岱尔高中参加了一个州际范围内的艺术比赛\N{\fnArial\fs18}Lawndale High is participating in a state-wide student art contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.38,0:02:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们选择在美术课上来宣布这个消息\N{\fnArial\fs18}That's why we chosen art class is the place to announce it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.97,0:02:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这个比赛的主题是"千禧年初期的学生生活"\N{\fnArial\fs18}The theme of the contest is "Student Life at the Dawn of the Millennium."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.80,0:02:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,就是在这个日新月异的年代 高中学生的生活是怎样的\N{\fnArial\fs18}What's it like to be a high school student in today's fast-changing world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.99,0:02:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,当然 是否参加完全出于自愿 但说实话\N{\fnArial\fs18}Entry is strictly voluntary, of course, although frankly,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.17,0:02:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为你们都不应该放弃这个难得的机会\N{\fnArial\fs18}I don't see how any of you could think of passing up the chance
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.93,0:02:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,为自己和朗岱尔高中"到来"荣誉\N{\fnArial\fs18}to bring honor unto yourself and Lawndale High.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.11,0:02:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,到来?\N{\fnArial\fs18}"Unto"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.17,0:02:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,系好我鞋带\N{\fnArial\fs18}Buckle my shoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.17,0:02:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs24\an8}出自小说名《One, two, buckle my shoe.》
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.71,0:02:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Defoe老师将从每个班里挑选出参赛作品\N{\fnArial\fs18}Ms. Defoe will choose the entries from each art class,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.42,0:02:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,而我则是我们学校这次比赛的协调员\N{\fnArial\fs18}and I'm contest coordinator for the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.98,0:02:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你们好运 孩子们\N{\fnArial\fs18}Good luck, kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.00,0:02:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,同学们 我劝你们还是好好把握这次机会\N{\fnArial\fs18}Students, I urge you to take this opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.89,0:02:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好奇心 探索精神 表达方式\N{\fnArial\fs18}Curiosity... inquiry... expression...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.36,0:03:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这些都是教育过程中的主要模块\N{\fnArial\fs18}these are the building blocks of education.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.77,0:03:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,校长?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.40,0:03:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,没有提问环节 祝你们好运\N{\fnArial\fs18}No questions! Good luck, all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.60,0:03:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我想告诉她我有个很好的做海报的主意\N{\fnArial\fs18}I wanted to tell her I've got a great idea for a poster!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.40,0:03:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是\N{\fnArial\fs18}Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.34,0:03:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我的主意是关于拉拉队的\N{\fnArial\fs18}Mine's going to be about cheerleading.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.42,0:03:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不 那我要做什么?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, no! Now what'll I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,来橄榄球队担任四分卫怎么样 宝贝?\N{\fnArial\fs18}How about something on quarterbacks, babe?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.07,0:03:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Jane 你可以留下来几分钟吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Jane, can you stay a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.61,0:03:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Jane 我很想知道所有的学生对这个比赛有什么看法\N{\fnArial\fs18}Jane, I'm eager to see what all the students come up with for this contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.38,0:03:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是所有那些选择参加的学生吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}All the students who choose to participate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.78,0:03:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,但我实在等不及想要看到你参加\N{\fnArial\fs18}But I really can't wait to see your entry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.42,0:03:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 你知道 我不认为艺术家们之间要互相竞赛\N{\fnArial\fs18}Well, you know, I really don't think artists should compete with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.19,0:03:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我只相信社区创造力\N{\fnArial\fs18}See, I believe in a community of creativity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.03,0:03:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你是一个杰出的艺术家和一个原创型思考者\N{\fnArial\fs18}You're such an accomplished artist, and such an original thinker.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.97,0:03:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,如果说这个学校谁能捕捉到当今学生的生活状况\N{\fnArial\fs18}If there's anyone in this school who can capture student life today,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.42,0:03:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那个人就是你\N{\fnArial\fs18}it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.44,0:03:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想说 祝你好运\N{\fnArial\fs18}I just want to say, good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.39,0:03:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fnArial\fs18}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.11,0:03:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,她干嘛要表现那么亲和?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Why did she have to be so nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.42,0:03:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,弄得我必须要想出些关于学生生活的愚蠢海报\N{\fnArial\fs18}Now I have to come up with some stupid poster about student life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.92,0:03:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,该从哪开始呢?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Where to start?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.15,0:03:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,有那么多令我们憎恨的地方\N{\fnArial\fs18}There's so much to hate about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.90,0:04:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,话说 没有人说一定要传达正面信息\N{\fnArial\fs18}You know, nobody said the message had to be positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.56,0:04:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我要做一些真正能够反映学生生活的海报\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm going to do something that really represents student life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.71,0:04:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.36,0:04:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉人们高中生活是有多操蛋\N{\fnArial\fs18}And tell the truth about how much it can suck
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.50,0:04:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.98,0:04:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,驱散掉那些故事书里所幻想的"年轻真好"的屁话\N{\fnArial\fs18}To blow away the story-book fantasy about how great it is to be young.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.29,0:04:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.06,0:04:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你要帮我一把\N{\fnArial\fs18}And you're going to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.16,0:04:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不要\N{\fnArial\fs18}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.99,0:04:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定要帮我一把\N{\fnArial\fs18}You gotta help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.14,0:04:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我认识最消极的人\N{\fnArial\fs18}You're the most negative person I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.80,0:04:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢夸奖\N{\fnArial\fs18}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样嘛\N{\fnArial\fs18}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.76,0:04:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,难得有机会能告诉全世界\N{\fnArial\fs18}Now's your chance to tell the world
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.00,0:04:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你真心认为朗岱尔高中生活何等鸟样\N{\fnArial\fs18}what you really think of life at Lawndale High.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.94,0:04:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉世界 我 Daria Morgendorffer 有话要说\N{\fnArial\fs18}Tell the world that I, Daria Morgendorffer, have something I want to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.06,0:04:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.92,0:04:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不要\N{\fnArial\fs18}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.64,0:04:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,来嘛 帮我一把\N{\fnArial\fs18}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.17,0:04:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.45,0:04:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我会做出我的个人陈述 并坚定不移地支持它\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'll make my personal statement, and I'll stand behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.28,0:04:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你会的\N{\fnArial\fs18}I knew you would.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.13,0:04:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,但只在完全匿名的情况下\N{\fnArial\fs18}But only on condition of strict anonymity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.07,0:04:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你才是真正的圣女贞德啊 你知道吗\N{\fnArial\fs18}You're a real Joan of Arc, you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.12,0:04:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs24\an8}贞德被英国宗教法庭判为异教徒 绑在火柱上烧死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.12,0:04:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧 而且我觉得我离火柱不远了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yeah, and I think I just ordered a stake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.65,0:04:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你看取名"美国未来的接班人"怎么样?\N{\fnArial\fs18}How about we call it, "America's Future Leaders,"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.49,0:04:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要做的就是把Kevin和Brittany的照片放大\N{\fnArial\fs18}and we just enlarge a picture of Kevin and Brittany?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.79,0:05:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,少来 那也太令人沮丧了吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}Come on, that's too depressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.96,0:05:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得我们叫它\N{\fnArial\fs18}How about we call it,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.18,0:05:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,"美丽只存在于肌肤深处" 然后我们贴上学生真正的皮肤?\N{\fnArial\fs18}"Beauty is only Skin Deep," and we attach the skin of an actual student?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.84,0:05:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这个我喜欢\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, I like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.47,0:05:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我在想能否劝Quinn把她的皮捐出来?\N{\fnArial\fs18}I wonder if we can talk Quinn into donating hers?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.86,0:05:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我开始在想这应该会需要很多的披萨\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm starting to think this is going to require more pizza.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.62,0:05:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我开始同意你的看法了\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm starting to agree with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.68,0:05:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我们说到哪了?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Where were we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.13,0:05:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我们说到挂一卷捕蝇纸 然后称它为\N{\fnArial\fs18}We were talking about hanging a roll of fly paper and calling it,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,"拥有吸引力的重要性"\N{\fnArial\fs18}"It's Important to Be Attractive."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.75,0:05:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那上面挂苍蝇还是不挂?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, yeah. With or without flies?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.89,0:05:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他们有在披萨配料中多加了一夸脱油脂吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Did they add another quart of grease to the pizza recipe?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.31,0:05:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,要再来一块吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}One more slice?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.93,0:05:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不要了 我真觉得我快要吐了\N{\fnArial\fs18}No, I already feel like I might throw up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.61,0:05:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,见到那么多人参加这次比赛 我真的感到很高兴\N{\fnArial\fs18}Well, it's very gratifying to see so much participation in the contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.43,0:05:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Charles 你海报的名字叫什么?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Charles, what's the name of your poster?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.30,0:05:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫它"开起 Chucky 开起"\N{\fnArial\fs18}I call it, "Ride, Chucky, Ride."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.86,0:05:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,它到底反映了现代学生生活的哪部分呢?\N{\fnArial\fs18}And what exactly does it say about student life at the century's edge?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.76,0:05:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这反映更多的是个人的目标陈述\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's more of a personal mission statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.60,0:06:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,他是指不可能实现的目标\N{\fnArial\fs18}Mission impossible, he means.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.87,0:06:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,给我们讲讲你的海报 Brittany\N{\fnArial\fs18}Tell us about your poster, Brittany.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.89,0:06:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我把它称做"拒绝饮酒与吸毒"\N{\fnArial\fs18}I call it, "Don't Drink or Take Drugs."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.30,0:06:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,所反映的信息是 拒绝饮酒和吸毒\N{\fnArial\fs18}And the message is, don't drink or take drugs!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.79,0:06:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们怎么看得出它的意思呢?\N{\fnArial\fs18}But how do we get that message?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.56,0:06:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到的只有酒精和毒品\N{\fnArial\fs18}All I see is the alcohol and the drugs,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.24,0:06:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,并没有什么否认标志说明它们的危险性啊\N{\fnArial\fs18}with no negative imagery to symbolize their dangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.08,0:06:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,有了\N{\fnArial\fs18}There!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.08,0:06:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Brittany 这... 我们还是下课后再讨论吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}Well, Brittany, that's... um... let's talk after class.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.18,0:06:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Jane 你们打算怎么做?\N{\fnArial\fs18}And Jane, what did you decide?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.46,0:06:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,她真漂亮\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, she's beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.78,0:06:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,"她知道自己完爆别人了 没人敢比她更瘦\N{\fnArial\fs18}"She knows she's a winner, she couldn't be thinner,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.99,0:06:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,于是她进了洗手间把吃的晚饭都吐了出来?"\N{\fnArial\fs18}now she goes in the bathroom and vomits up dinner?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Jane 我觉得这并不好笑\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, Jane, I don't think that's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.51,0:06:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你不觉得吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Um, you don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你认为拿有饮食失调的人来作乐很搞笑吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Do you think it's funny to make fun of someone with an eating disorder?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.24,0:06:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不 但是...\N{\fnArial\fs18}No! But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.98,0:06:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这本来就不是拿来作乐的\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's not meant to be funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.95,0:06:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这本来就不是拿来作乐的\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's not meant to be funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.32,0:06:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 那么\N{\fnArial\fs18}Well, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.25,0:06:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那你是要表达对一些形象比较不佳的人的偏见\N{\fnArial\fs18}do you think it's your place to pass judgement on someone with a low self-image
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.38,0:07:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,仅仅因为你自己没有这些问题吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}just because you don't have that problem yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.84,0:07:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,但那根本不是我要说的啊\N{\fnArial\fs18}But that's not what I'm saying at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.61,0:07:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那你要说的是什么?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Then what are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.98,0:07:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我说的是人们不应该... 呃...\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm saying that people shouldn't... uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.92,0:07:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,她说的是现今太注重外貌是很危险的\N{\fnArial\fs18}She's saying that all the emphasis on appearance today can be dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.75,0:07:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这个女孩很漂亮\N{\fnArial\fs18}The girl is very pretty,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.40,0:07:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你的第一反应是"多快乐的青年啊"\N{\fnArial\fs18}and your first reaction is, "Oh, what a happy teenager!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.93,0:07:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但也许并不是你看到的那样\N{\fnArial\fs18}But maybe that's not the whole story.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.71,0:07:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,也许她们的美丽是要付出很高代价的\N{\fnArial\fs18}Maybe that prettiness comes at a price.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.01,0:07:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Jane 这就是你想说的吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, is that what you're saying, Jane?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.14,0:07:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}Pretty much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.08,0:07:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那你一定要以这种毫无吸引力的图解语言表达出来嘛\N{\fnArial\fs18}And you felt you had to say it in such graphic, unappealing language.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.70,0:07:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是有意选择这样的语言表达的\N{\fnArial\fs18}The choice of words was deliberate,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.59,0:07:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,为的是用这样的美丽形象吸引人\N{\fnArial\fs18}to contrast with the beauty of the image
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.80,0:07:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,然后给观者一种震撼 让他们警觉\N{\fnArial\fs18}and shock the viewer into paying attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.06,0:07:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗 Jane\N{\fnArial\fs18}You know what, Jane?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.64,0:07:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这真的是一件艺术品\N{\fnArial\fs18}This really is a work of art,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.76,0:07:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,而它也以一种很原始的方式做出了声明\N{\fnArial\fs18}and it really does make a statement, in an original way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.19,0:07:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你能带我和你们一起参加这个州际比赛\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'd like you to let me enter it in the state-wide competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.34,0:07:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,听起来不错\N{\fnArial\fs18}Sounds okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.49,0:07:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,那你的搭档有什么看法?\N{\fnArial\fs18}And how does it sound to your collaborator?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.58,0:07:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,下次我会给你一个提前准备好的声明\N{\fnArial\fs18}Next time, I give you a prepared statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.61,0:08:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria Jane 这张海报真漂亮\N{\fnArial\fs18}Daria, Jane. This poster is beautiful
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.03,0:08:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,真是一幅杰作啊\N{\fnArial\fs18}Truly accomplished.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.50,0:08:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你们的荣誉 也是朗岱尔高中的荣誉\N{\fnArial\fs18}A real credit to yourselves and to Lawndale High.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.83,0:08:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,还有那几句诗... 非常的抽象有趣\N{\fnArial\fs18}And the poem... a very interesting perspective.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.88,0:08:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,除了...\N{\fnArial\fs18}Except...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,除了什么?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.21,0:08:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,其中有一句\N{\fnArial\fs18}There's this one line.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.73,0:08:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.70,0:08:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我在想你们能否考虑\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm just wondering if you would consider
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.98,0:08:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,把"晚饭都吐出来"那部分改改\N{\fnArial\fs18}changing the part about vomiting up dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.20,0:08:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那有点恶心\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's kind of yucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.64,0:08:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,它会表现出一种不雅的学生形象\N{\fnArial\fs18}It presents a distasteful picture to the student body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.16,0:08:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我们并不希望人们那样做\N{\fnArial\fs18}You know we wouldn't want people doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.93,0:08:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,有道理\N{\fnArial\fs18}That's the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.20,0:08:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们的意见一致咯\N{\fnArial\fs18}So we're all on the same page!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.78,0:08:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这个女孩太过于追求美丽\N{\fnArial\fs18}The girl is so obsessed with being beautiful
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.64,0:08:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,导致她在某一方面变得很极端\N{\fnArial\fs18}that it turns her into something really ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.61,0:08:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是海报要表达的意思\N{\fnArial\fs18}That's the message of the poster.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.52,0:08:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,花了我好一段时间构思呢\N{\fnArial\fs18}So it takes me a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.06,0:08:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,但她看起来既美丽又快乐啊\N{\fnArial\fs18}But she looks so pretty and happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.68,0:08:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,何不把主题表现得积极乐观呢?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Why not make the theme positive?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.64,0:08:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,去掉"把吃的晚饭都吐了出来"\N{\fnArial\fs18}Instead of "she vomits up dinner,"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.64,0:08:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,换成"她几乎没有动过晚餐"\N{\fnArial\fs18}how about "she barely touches dinner?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.45,0:08:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说保持美丽太累了 以至于她根本没力气去吃东西了?\N{\fnArial\fs18}You mean, being that gorgeous is so tiring that she's too exhausted to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.49,0:08:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这个意思\N{\fnArial\fs18}Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.43,0:08:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,看吧 就算美丽的人也有烦恼\N{\fnArial\fs18}See, even beautiful people have problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.42,0:08:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 就围绕这个主题 孩子们\N{\fnArial\fs18}So, hang in there, kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.26,0:08:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你完全没了解我所表达的意思 对吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}Boy, you really don't get it at all, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.47,0:08:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 我压根儿就不想写这些愚蠢的诗\N{\fnArial\fs18}Look, I didn't even want to write this stupid poem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.50,0:09:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不在乎人们怎么对他们自己呢\N{\fnArial\fs18}I don't care about what other people do to themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.92,0:09:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但是如果你改了那句\N{\fnArial\fs18}But if you change that line,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.44,0:09:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这首诗就变成传达另外一种虚伪的信息了\N{\fnArial\fs18}the poem becomes just another phony dishonest message.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,它传达的和原来所传达的一样\N{\fnArial\fs18}It'll applaud the same thing it criticized before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.00,0:09:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你难道没看出来吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Don't you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.44,0:09:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Morgendorffer小姐\N{\fnArial\fs18}Ms. Morgendorffer,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.54,0:09:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,年轻人看起来太骄傲不太好吧?\N{\fnArial\fs18}is it so wrong for young people to take pride in the way they look?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.64,0:09:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,对这张海报 你想怎样就怎样吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}Do whatever you want to the poster.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.35,0:09:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不要写我的名字就好\N{\fnArial\fs18}Just take my name off it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.02,0:09:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,还有我的\N{\fnArial\fs18}And mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.87,0:09:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,别急 小姐们 你们好像有点太激动了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Now, now, ladies. Emotions are running high.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.72,0:09:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我们花一天时间好好想想 你们看怎样?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Let's all take 24 hours to think about it, hmmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.17,0:09:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.43,0:09:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你们自己做决定吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's your decision to make!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.44,0:09:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,打电话给她们父母\N{\fnArial\fs18}Call their parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.41,0:09:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Jane Lane Amanda Lane女士\N{\fnArial\fs18}Jane Lane. Mrs. Amanda Lane.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.89,0:09:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你好吗 Lane女士\N{\fnArial\fs18}"Hello, Mrs. Lane!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.07,0:09:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,没人接 那就打给Helen Morgendorffer\N{\fnArial\fs18}Okay. Helen Morgendorffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.97,0:10:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 Morgendorffer女士\N{\fnArial\fs18}"Hello, Mrs. Morgendorffer!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.73,0:10:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我三点钟完全没有事要做\N{\fnArial\fs18}I've got absolutely no paperwork for my three o'clock,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.28,0:10:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这个早上我都没有动力工作了\N{\fnArial\fs18}I can't find the brief I was supposed to get this morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.49,0:10:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,还有我记录里的电邮地址还是错的\N{\fnArial\fs18}and my stationary still has the wrong e-mail address!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.25,0:10:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,为毛这里没有一件事是顺心的?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Why the hell can't anything ever go right around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.07,0:10:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Helen? 是你女儿的老师\N{\fnArial\fs18}Helen? It's your daughter's teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.80,0:10:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉他们我会让Quinn在星期一把作业交上去\N{\fnArial\fs18}Tell them I'll make sure Quinn turns in the assignment by Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.99,0:10:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,顺便问问作业是什么 好吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, and try to find out what the assignment is, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.52,0:10:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,或者你可以开始记录下来\N{\fnArial\fs18}and maybe you could get started making a few notes on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.08,0:10:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,是你另一个女儿 应该\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's your other daughter, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.45,0:10:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria? 那好吧 告诉他们我会说说她的态度的\N{\fnArial\fs18}Daria? Well, then, tell them I'll talk to her about her attitude,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.32,0:10:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,顺便问问她侮辱了谁 又说了什么\N{\fnArial\fs18}and try to find out who she insulted and what she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.54,0:10:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他说她有个很好的机会\N{\fnArial\fs18}He says that she has a rare opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.36,0:10:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不想看到您女儿白白浪费掉\N{\fnArial\fs18}that he'd hate to see her squander...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.87,0:10:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,电话给我 你好 我是Helen Morgendorffer\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, just give it to me. Helen Morgendorffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.56,0:10:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 Morgenfoffer女士 Morgendorffer\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hello, Mrs. Morgenfoffer... uh, Morgendorffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.45,0:10:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我是朗岱尔高中的Timothy O'Neill\N{\fnArial\fs18}This is Timothy O'Neill at Lawndale High.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.89,0:10:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我是您女儿Daria的英语老师\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm your daughter Daria's English teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.74,0:10:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 请问是关于...\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yes, is this about her essay
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.08,0:10:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,她《废除死刑而采取酷刑》的论文吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}banning capital punishment and bringing back torture instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.68,0:11:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,很明显她只是在开笑话\N{\fnArial\fs18}Because that was obviously a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.47,0:11:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不 Morgendorffer女士 是关于她帮忙创作的一幅海报\N{\fnArial\fs18}No, Mrs. Morgendorffer, it's about a poster she helped create.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.62,0:11:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我们正在举行一个...\N{\fnArial\fs18}See, we're having a contest
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.06,0:11:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,关于千禧年初期的学生生活...\N{\fnArial\fs18}concerning student life at the dawn of the millennium...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.44,0:11:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,请你能说快一点吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Could you possibly speed this up a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.24,0:11:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我快错过两个电话会议了\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm late for two conference calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.17,0:11:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,她给一幅很好的图片写了一段不太好的诗歌\N{\fnArial\fs18}Um, she wrote a very unpleasant poem to go with a very nice picture
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.38,0:11:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,希望您能跟她谈谈 也许能让她考虑重新写一段\N{\fnArial\fs18}and I was hoping you would talk to her about maybe reconsidering and rewriting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.93,0:11:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 我很乐意\N{\fnArial\fs18}Fine, I'll be happy to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.25,0:11:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,如果这件事还需要进一步讨论 请你致电给我丈夫吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}If this requires further discussion, please feel free to call my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.55,0:11:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Jake Morgendorffer\N{\fnArial\fs18}Jake Morgendorffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.97,0:11:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 Morgendorffer先生\N{\fnArial\fs18}"Hello, Mr. Morgendorffer."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.76,0:11:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 我是Jake Morgendorffer Jake Morgendorffer在这里\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hello Jake Morgendorffer, Jake Morgendorffer here,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.78,0:11:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,能为您做点什么? 有人在吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}what can I do for you, anybody there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.89,0:11:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你好?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.92,0:11:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,您已接通"咨询Jake Morgendorffer"的办公室\N{\fnArial\fs18}You've reached the office of Jake Morgendorffer Consulting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.10,0:11:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要咨询人士帮助\N{\fnArial\fs18}You need to be consulted
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.52,0:11:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,谁还要一勺香蒜酱?\N{\fnArial\fs18}More penne a la pesto, anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.68,0:11:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.58,0:11:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你的朋友Jane叫你帮她一起制作海报\N{\fnArial\fs18}You friend Jane asked you to help her make a poster.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.98,0:11:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,如果发现是哪个虐待狂今天打电话给我...\N{\fnArial\fs18}If I ever find out who the sadist was who called today...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.34,0:11:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你想出了关于一个饮食失调的漂亮女生的主意\N{\fnArial\fs18}You came up with the idea of a pretty girl with an eating disorder.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.42,0:11:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是滴\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.96,0:12:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria 那真是太... 你了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Daria, that is so... you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.20,0:12:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这是种赞美还是侮辱?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Is that a compliment or an insult?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.58,0:12:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,话说 如果把这个冻在冰箱里\N{\fnArial\fs18}You know, if you refrigerate this stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.16,0:12:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,香蒜酱会变得有点发臭\N{\fnArial\fs18}the pesto kinda gets a little funky.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.63,0:12:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,会氧化或发生别的化学变化\N{\fnArial\fs18}It oxidizes or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.16,0:12:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,最好是当天做了当天吃\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's best eaten the day it's made.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.17,0:12:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,谁还想再要一些?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Now, who would like some more?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.41,0:12:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Jake 你能把那该死通心粉放下吗\N{\fnArial\fs18}Jake, would you put down the damn macaroni
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.59,0:12:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,问下你女儿为什么她一定总是要那么愤世嫉俗\N{\fnArial\fs18}and ask your daughter why she has to be so cynical all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.45,0:12:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是通心粉 Helen\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's not macaroni, Helen!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.96,0:12:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,她本来应该做一幅有关学生生活的海报\N{\fnArial\fs18}She's supposed to be making a poster about student life,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.60,0:12:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,但是她想的却是她能想出的最负面的信息\N{\fnArial\fs18}and she comes up with the most negative message she could think of.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.22,0:12:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这不叫负面\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's not negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.50,0:12:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这是正面 反映了学生不想被人单凭外表而断定他们\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's supportive of students who don't want to be judged by their looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.99,0:12:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,算了吧 Daria 那样的人根本不存在\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, come on Daria. People like that don't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.32,0:12:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Jake 问问她为什么就不能偶尔积极乐观一点\N{\fnArial\fs18}Jake, ask her why she can't be upbeat once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.86,0:12:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你看 Helen\N{\fnArial\fs18}You see, Helen,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.96,0:12:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,如果这是通心粉和芝士 那将会多糟糕啊\N{\fnArial\fs18}if this was supposed to be macaroni and cheese, it would be very bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.90,0:12:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但这是香蒜酱\N{\fnArial\fs18}But it's penne a la pesto,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.50,0:12:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,如果以香蒜酱的标准去评判 这一盆可是极好的\N{\fnArial\fs18}and judged by the standards of penne a la pesto, it's very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.80,0:12:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Jake 你到底在说什么? 你有认真听吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Jake, what the hell are you talking about? Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.68,0:12:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,当然有\N{\fnArial\fs18}Of course, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.70,0:12:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是\N{\fnArial\fs18}What I mean is,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.14,0:12:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,如果这是一幅提高学生生活的宣传海报 那真是太糟糕了\N{\fnArial\fs18}if this poster is supposed to be propaganda promoting student life, it's very bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.57,0:12:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果它作为一种表达Daria对学生生活的个人观点的艺术\N{\fnArial\fs18}But if it's supposed to be art expressing Daria's personal vision of student life,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.86,0:13:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那很棒 你觉得呢?\N{\fnArial\fs18}it's very good. See?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.03,0:13:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,谢了 老爸\N{\fnArial\fs18}Thanks, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.21,0:13:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,在氧化了\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's oxidizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.88,0:13:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样 啪\N{\fnArial\fs18}So then, splat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.58,0:13:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,倒在了我爸头上 晚饭结束了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Dinner ends up on top of my dad's head.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.88,0:13:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Wow, excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.51,0:13:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你的年少轻狂正在将你的家庭撕裂\N{\fnArial\fs18}Your youthful integrity is tearing your family apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.23,0:13:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,并不全是\N{\fnArial\fs18}Well, not exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.59,0:13:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我妈回来跟我叨念了什么经前不快症状 跟我道歉了\N{\fnArial\fs18}My mother came back and mumbled something about PMS and apologized,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.70,0:13:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但至少我们今晚不用吃剩下的通心粉了\N{\fnArial\fs18}but at least we don't have to eat leftover macaroni tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.25,0:13:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还在坚持退出那个海报比赛 对吧?\N{\fnArial\fs18}We're still resigning from the poster contest, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.35,0:13:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Daira?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Daria?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.43,0:13:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉他们我至少会听O'Neill先生的意见\N{\fnArial\fs18}I told them I'd at least listen to Mr. O'Neill's point of view,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.46,0:13:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,但我并没有做出任何承诺\N{\fnArial\fs18}but I didn't make any promises.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.90,0:13:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 除了那个之外\N{\fnArial\fs18}I mean, other than that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.54,0:13:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你们看 我并没想要改变你们对这幅海报原本的意图\N{\fnArial\fs18}So you see, girls, I don't want to change the intent of your poster.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.94,0:13:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,只是想让它更积极和谐一点\N{\fnArial\fs18}I just want to make it more palatable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.46,0:13:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,就像他们说的 一勺糖能帮助你把苦药吃下去\N{\fnArial\fs18}You know what they say, a spoonful of sugar helps the medicine go down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.89,0:13:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你有糖尿病那就不管用了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Not if you're diabetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.29,0:13:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,打断下 O'Neill先生\N{\fnArial\fs18}Excuse me, Mr. O'Neill?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.53,0:13:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Uh, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.68,0:13:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要用我的新海报参加比赛\N{\fnArial\fs18}I want to enter my new poster in the contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.79,0:14:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这张真是不错\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, that's really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.51,0:14:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,表达出多积极的信息啊 是团结主题吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}What an affirmative message. Togetherness?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.11,0:14:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,表达的信息是 "不要加入帮派"\N{\fnArial\fs18}Um, the message is, "don't join a gang."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.57,0:14:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这也是标题\N{\fnArial\fs18}That's also the title.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.36,0:14:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Brittany 我看到了帮派\N{\fnArial\fs18}Um, Brittany, I see the gang,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.02,0:14:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,但貌似没看到有什么东西表明了"不要"\N{\fnArial\fs18}but I don't see anything representing "don't."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.26,0:14:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是嘛\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.80,0:14:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我唇膏哪去了?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Where's my lipstick?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.31,0:14:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,也是好作品变成牛逼作品的利器\N{\fnArial\fs18}And that's how good art becomes great art.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.12,0:14:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不管怎样 我有个主意\N{\fnArial\fs18}Anyway, I have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.12,0:14:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不如你们让我来写这段话如何?\N{\fnArial\fs18}How about you let me work on the poem a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我能想出一些比较没那么伤人...\N{\fnArial\fs18}Maybe I can come up with something that's less abrasive,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.38,0:14:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,而且符合你们意思的句子\N{\fnArial\fs18}that gets your point across.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.73,0:14:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们不喜欢你想的怎么办?\N{\fnArial\fs18}And if we don't like what you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.29,0:14:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那就不用管它了 就让它按照你们原来设想的那样做\N{\fnArial\fs18}Then we'll forget about it and leave the poster the way you made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.65,0:14:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你们怎样都不吃亏 好不好?\N{\fnArial\fs18}You can't lose. What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.39,0:14:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs24\an8}迪士尼影史上获奥斯卡成就最高的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.39,0:14:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 但要是再引用《欢乐满人间》就不跟你玩了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Okay, but quote Mary Poppins again and the deal's off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.71,0:14:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Lane小姐 Morgendorffer小姐\N{\fnArial\fs18}Ms. Lane and Ms. Morgendorffer,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.05,0:14:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,相信你们一定会对O'Neill先生即将展示给你们看的感到满意\N{\fnArial\fs18}I believe you're going to be pleased with what Mr. O'Neill has to show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.67,0:14:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria Jane 我真觉得我做到了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Daria, Jane, I really think I've done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.00,0:14:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我把那个较粗糙的部分变得更柔和\N{\fnArial\fs18}I've captured the essence of your message
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.86,0:15:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,抓住了你们要表达的意思的实质\N{\fnArial\fs18}while softening the rough edges.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.97,0:15:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你砂洗过它?\N{\fnArial\fs18}You stone-washed it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.26,0:15:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,"她知道自己完爆别人了 没人敢比她更瘦"\N{\fnArial\fs18}"She knows she's a winner, she couldn't be thinner,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.02,0:15:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,因为她对于早中晚三餐所吃的东西都很谨慎\N{\fnArial\fs18}cause she's careful what she eats for breakfast, lunch, and dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.22,0:15:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,合理膳食万岁"\N{\fnArial\fs18}Good nutrition rules."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.00,0:15:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你在开玩笑吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Is this a joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.30,0:15:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,合理膳食习惯可不是笑话 Daria\N{\fnArial\fs18}Smart eating habits are no joke, Daria.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.48,0:15:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这跟我们的海报有毛关系?\N{\fnArial\fs18}What does this have to do with out poster?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.70,0:15:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,把要传达的消极信息变成了积极信息\N{\fnArial\fs18}It turns a negative message into a positive one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.17,0:15:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,她不漂亮是因为她经常不吃东西\N{\fnArial\fs18}She's not pretty because she starves herself into it,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.94,0:15:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,她很漂亮是因为她爱护她自己\N{\fnArial\fs18}she's pretty because she takes care of herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.58,0:15:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这比原来的表达更有力 因为非常的积极乐观\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's even more powerful than before, because it's upbeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.24,0:15:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我懂了 她再也不会吐了\N{\fnArial\fs18}I see. She's not going to throw up anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.20,0:15:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,但我可能会\N{\fnArial\fs18}But I might.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.17,0:15:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,别那样做\N{\fnArial\fs18}Don't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.30,0:15:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那很负面消极\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's downbeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.63,0:15:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你们这些年轻人应该感谢O'Neill先生\N{\fnArial\fs18}You young women should be thanking Mr. O'Neill
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.98,0:15:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦把你们想表达的信息有所保留\N{\fnArial\fs18}for his hard work preserving your message.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.67,0:15:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他没有保留它 他是歪曲了它\N{\fnArial\fs18}He didn't preserve it. He perverted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.59,0:15:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,他把所有实质和影响 变成了没有意义的废话\N{\fnArial\fs18}He removed all the substance and impact and turned it into meaningless drivel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.14,0:15:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只想要回我们原来的作品\N{\fnArial\fs18}So we'd like our poster back now, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.09,0:15:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Meaning what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.02,0:15:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,意思是 根据我们的协议 我们要退出这个比赛\N{\fnArial\fs18}Meaning we're withdrawing it from the contest, according to our agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.85,0:15:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起小姐们 我可没有做出任何协议\N{\fnArial\fs18}Excuse me, girls, I didn't make any agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.49,0:15:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,O'Neill先生做了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Mr. O'Neill did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.60,0:16:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,O'Neill先生没资格跟你们做出这样的协议\N{\fnArial\fs18}Mr. O'Neill is in no position to offer such a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.40,0:16:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这个海报会在明晚的学校董事会会议中展出\N{\fnArial\fs18}The poster will be displayed during the school board meeting tomorrow night
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.06,0:16:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,然后将会拿去参加比赛\N{\fnArial\fs18}then it will be entered into the contest,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.34,0:16:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,最终给你们和我们带来荣...\N{\fnArial\fs18}and it will bring honor and acclaim to you two and to our...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.15,0:16:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,但Li校长 我确实保证...\N{\fnArial\fs18}But Ms. Li, I did promise...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.31,0:16:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我没保证\N{\fnArial\fs18}I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.25,0:16:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,她可以那样做吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Can she do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.29,0:16:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不能 这都是太多的香蒜味通心粉带来的噩梦\N{\fnArial\fs18}No, this is all a horrible dream brought on by too much penne a la pesto.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.96,0:16:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不要寻求帮助或什么吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Don't we have a recourse or anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.56,0:16:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,能和O'Neill先生谈谈吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Can we talk to Mr. O'Neill?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以说服他\N{\fnArial\fs18}We could appeal to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.32,0:16:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,或许他会用他的压倒性人格压倒Li校长\N{\fnArial\fs18}and he might turn the full force of his overwhelming personality on Ms. Li,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.86,0:16:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,然后 她会把他吃掉\N{\fnArial\fs18}and then she'd eat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.60,0:16:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那找你父母怎么样?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Well, how about your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.55,0:16:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,找你父母怎样?\N{\fnArial\fs18}How about yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.92,0:16:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我妈现在有点忙\N{\fnArial\fs18}My mother's a little preoccupied right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.22,0:16:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,她在追踪干燥室里不明热气变化的来源\N{\fnArial\fs18}She's tracking down the source of a disturbing heat variation in her kiln.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.80,0:16:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,但你妈妈可是个律师\N{\fnArial\fs18}But your mother is a lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.88,0:16:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,一个认为我去参加这个海报比赛...\N{\fnArial\fs18}A lawyer who thinks it's a really good idea
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.88,0:16:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是一个很好主意的律师\N{\fnArial\fs18}for me to get involved in the poster contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.35,0:16:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,制度太让人失望了\N{\fnArial\fs18}The system failed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.63,0:16:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,去他的制度\N{\fnArial\fs18}The system sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.57,0:16:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须从制度外出发\N{\fnArial\fs18}We're going to have to go outside the system.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.22,0:16:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你的意思不是...\N{\fnArial\fs18}You don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.72,0:16:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那个意思\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.10,0:16:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这事找我 你们算是找对人了\N{\fnArial\fs18}You did the right thing coming to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.68,0:17:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉把你吵醒了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Sorry we woke you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.51,0:17:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系\N{\fnArial\fs18}Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.90,0:17:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这也是迟早发生的事\N{\fnArial\fs18}It was bound to happen sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.62,0:17:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 计划是这样的\N{\fnArial\fs18}All right, here's the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.98,0:17:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我会坐在这里随时准备加大马力踩油门\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'll sit right here with my foot on the accelerator, ready to burn rubber.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.28,0:17:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Trent 把车熄火放到那边\N{\fnArial\fs18}Trent, pull over here and make sure you turn off the car
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.72,0:17:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,小心你睡着了 好吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}in case you fall asleep, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.77,0:17:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,B计划 酷\N{\fnArial\fs18}Alternate plan. Cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.26,0:17:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs24\an8}海报大赛参赛作品
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.51,0:17:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,警报解除了吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}All clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.55,0:17:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,准备解除\N{\fnArial\fs18}Just about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.00,0:17:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\fnArial\fs18}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.81,0:17:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你们两个在这儿干嘛?\N{\fnArial\fs18}What are you guys doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.66,0:17:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,观察\N{\fnArial\fs18}Observing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.81,0:17:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,清白的\N{\fnArial\fs18}Innocently.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.71,0:17:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,真不敢相信Li校长对你们海报所做的事\N{\fnArial\fs18}I can't believe what Ms. Li did to your poster.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.18,0:17:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,等等... 你们两个想要干什么?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Wait a minute... what are you guys planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.20,0:17:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,走开 Landon\N{\fnArial\fs18}Get lost, Landon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.27,0:17:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,为你自身考虑\N{\fnArial\fs18}For your own good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.28,0:17:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你前程大好 妹子\N{\fnArial\fs18}You've got a bright future, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.78,0:17:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你不想在这儿跟着一些将要变坏的东西一起变坏吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}You don't want to be here when what's going to go down goes down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.71,0:17:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我们行动吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.28,0:17:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事?!\N{\fnArial\fs18}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.89,0:17:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.06,0:18:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你们真以为你们可以逃脱掉责任吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Did you really think you were going to get away with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.61,0:18:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,现在说"可以"是很愚蠢的吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}Well, it would be stupid to say "yes" now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.17,0:18:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我没开玩笑\N{\fnArial\fs18}This is no joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.40,0:18:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,故意毁坏学校财产是会受到惩罚的犯罪\N{\fnArial\fs18}Vandalizing school property is a punishable offense,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.13,0:18:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要做的第一件事就是打电话给你们父母\N{\fnArial\fs18}and the first thing we're going to do is call your parents!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.95,0:18:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,算了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, bother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.05,0:18:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,在这周边 我应该拍谁的马屁\N{\fnArial\fs18}Whose butt do I have to kiss around here
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.22,0:18:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,才能在傍晚前拿到我的局间邮件?\N{\fnArial\fs18}to get my interoffice mail before nightfall?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.19,0:18:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Helen 是你女儿学校的校长打来的\N{\fnArial\fs18}Helen? It's your daughter's school. The principal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.71,0:18:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,校长?\N{\fnArial\fs18}The principal?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.35,0:18:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.56,0:18:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 Morgendorffer女士\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hello, Mrs. Morgendorffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.82,0:18:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我是Angela Li 朗岱尔高中的校长\N{\fnArial\fs18}This is Angela Li, principal of Lawndale High.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.78,0:18:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 Li校长 请问有什么能帮你?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yes, Ms. Li. How may I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.00,0:18:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Morgendorffer女士 恐怕我有一些坏消息要告诉你\N{\fnArial\fs18}Mrs. Morgendorffer, I'm afraid I have some rather bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.96,0:18:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,您的女儿Daria 她涉嫌故意毁坏学校财产\N{\fnArial\fs18}Your daughter, Daria, appears to have been involved in an act of vandalism.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.44,0:18:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,什么?\N{\fnArial\fs18}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.23,0:18:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Morgendorffer女士\N{\fnArial\fs18}Mrs. Morgendorffer,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.20,0:18:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,您的女儿和Jane Lane一起\N{\fnArial\fs18}your daughter collaborated with Jane Lane
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.32,0:18:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,为一次艺术比赛创作了一幅海报\N{\fnArial\fs18}in the creation of a poster for our art contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.53,0:18:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我知道\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yes, I'm aware of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.84,0:19:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我们发现海报的一部分很不合宜\N{\fnArial\fs18}We found part of the poster unacceptable,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.86,0:19:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,所以在参赛前修改了一点\N{\fnArial\fs18}so it was altered prior to its entry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.10,0:19:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,很不幸的是 有人在海报展出的时候把它毁坏了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Unfortunately, someone defaced the poster while it was on display,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.60,0:19:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,考虑到您女儿还有Lane小姐曾反对修改这幅海报\N{\fnArial\fs18}and since your daughter and Ms. Lane had objected to changing it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.13,0:19:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我很确定他们就是损坏海报的人\N{\fnArial\fs18}I must assume that they were the vandals.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.52,0:19:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕我要对他们采取严厉的措施\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm afraid I'm going to have to take drastic action.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.50,0:19:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\fnArial\fs18}Wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.44,0:19:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你说她们曾经反对修改海报\N{\fnArial\fs18}You're saying the girls were against changing the poster,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.42,0:19:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,但还是让它去参加比赛了?\N{\fnArial\fs18}but entered it into the contest anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.16,0:19:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这是为她们着想\N{\fnArial\fs18}It was entered for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.70,0:19:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得这个比赛的参加是以自愿为原则的吧?\N{\fnArial\fs18}I was under the impression that participation in this contest was voluntary.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.13,0:19:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是自愿 但是您的女儿不自愿参加\N{\fnArial\fs18}It was, but your daughter refused to volunteer,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.38,0:19:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,按她的情况 我就得强制她参加了\N{\fnArial\fs18}so in her case, I made it mandatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.49,0:19:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 Li校长 让我这样跟你说吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}All right, Ms. Li, let me make sure I have this straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.55,0:19:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你把我女儿的海报拿走 修改了其中的意图\N{\fnArial\fs18}You took my daughter's poster from her, altered its content,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.70,0:19:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,在她不愿意的情况下拿去展览\N{\fnArial\fs18}exhibited it against her will,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.41,0:19:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,现在还要对她进行处分\N{\fnArial\fs18}and are now threatening discipline
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.58,0:19:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你说她毁坏了她自己的财产\N{\fnArial\fs18}because you claim she defaced her own property,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.85,0:19:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,就是你说的偷窃?\N{\fnArial\fs18}which you admit to stealing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.35,0:19:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这根本不是我要说的\N{\fnArial\fs18}That's not what I said at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.28,0:19:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Li校长 请问你对"侵犯公民自由"这个短语熟悉吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Ms. Li, are you familiar with the phrase "violation of civil liberties"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.37,0:19:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我...\N{\fnArial\fs18}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.96,0:19:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,还有"吃官司"\N{\fnArial\fs18}And the phrase "big fat lawsuit"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.81,0:20:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,所以唯一能拯救我们作品的方法就是毁掉它\N{\fnArial\fs18}So, the only way for us to save our work was to destroy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.00,0:20:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这话真上口\N{\fnArial\fs18}Catchy phrase.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.18,0:20:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,而且还不用受罚\N{\fnArial\fs18}And we got away with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.44,0:20:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该把这事写成一个小故事\N{\fnArial\fs18}You should turn this into a short story.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.30,0:20:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不失为一个好主意\N{\fnArial\fs18}That's not a bad idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.67,0:20:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我已经想好题目了\N{\fnArial\fs18}And I think I already have a title for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.93,0:20:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,什么题目?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.57,0:20:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我打算叫它 "千禧年初期的学生生活"\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm going to call it, "Student Life at the Dawn of the New Millennium."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.06,0:20:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,赢了 艺术比赛我赢了\N{\fnArial\fs18}I won! I won the art contest!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.54,0:20:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\fn迷你简汉真广标\fsp1\c&HE6ECE8&\pos(390,155)}欢迎微博关注\N\N{\fs28}@漫迪字幕组
